          <div class="cf-row"><div class="cf-icon">🔮</div><div><div class="cf-title">Tarot Archetype Matching</div><div class="cf-desc">Your Major Arcana archetype reveals your soul's journey and which archetypes create beautiful, lasting bonds.</div></div></div>
          <div class="cf-row"><div class="cf-icon">🔢</div><div><div class="cf-title">Numerology Life Path</div><div class="cf-desc">Life path, destiny, and soul urge numbers reveal deep compatibility and shared karmic lessons.</div></div></div>
          <div class="cf-row"><div class="cf-icon">🌙</div><div><div class="cf-title">Moon Phase Intelligence</div><div class="cf-desc">Real-time lunar cycle guidance for optimal moments to connect, date, and deepen a relationship.</div></div></div>
