<!-- FEATURES -->
<section id="features" class="section-pad" aria-labelledby="features-h">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto">
      <span class="section-label">App Features</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="features-h">Built for <em>Real Connection</em></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin:0 auto">Every feature moves you from matching to genuinely knowing someone.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <article class="feat-card reveal"><span class="feat-emoji">💬</span><div class="feat-title">AI Ice Breaker</div><p class="feat-desc">Never stare at a blank message box. AI suggests personalised conversation starters based on both your cosmic profiles and shared interests.</p></article>
      <article class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-1"><span class="feat-emoji">🔮</span><div class="feat-title">Daily Tarot Reading</div><p class="feat-desc">Every morning, draw your personalised tarot card with a love-focused reading. Know what cosmic energy is shaping your love life today.</p></article>
      <article class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-2"><span class="feat-emoji">🌙</span><div class="feat-title">Moon Phase Guide</div><p class="feat-desc">Real-time lunar notifications for the optimal moments to reach out, go on dates, or have important relationship conversations.</p></article>
      <article class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-3"><span class="feat-emoji">🎭</span><div class="feat-title">Compatibility Games</div><p class="feat-desc">Play interactive personality games with your matches before committing to connect. Getting to know someone should be genuinely fun.</p></article>
      <article class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-4"><span class="feat-emoji">👥</span><div class="feat-title">Friend Mode</div><p class="feat-desc">Not seeking romance? Find your cosmic best friend, travel companion, or business partner. simmmy honours all meaningful connections.</p></article>
      <article class="feat-card reveal"><span class="feat-emoji">🛡️</span><div class="feat-title">Verified Profiles</div><p class="feat-desc">Every profile is AI photo-verified. 24/7 moderation and instant reporting keep simmmy a genuinely safe, respectful space.</p></article>
      <article class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-1"><span class="feat-emoji">📖</span><div class="feat-title">Daily Cosmic Brief</div><p class="feat-desc">Your personalised planetary transit forecast every morning. Which energies are shaping your love life today? simmmy knows before you wake up.</p></article>
      <article class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-2"><span class="feat-emoji">🎵</span><div class="feat-title">Vibe Matching</div><p class="feat-desc">Connect Spotify to add a musical soul signature to your profile. Musical chemistry is a real, measurable dimension of compatibility.</p></article>
      <article class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-3"><span class="feat-emoji">🎪</span><div class="feat-title">Cosmic Events</div><p class="feat-desc">Attend curated singles events, astrology nights, and group activities matched to your zodiac sign and personality type. Real connection, cosmically guided.</p></article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
