<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq" class="section-pad" aria-labelledby="faq-h">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center">
    <div class="reveal"><span class="section-label">FAQs</span><h2 class="section-title" id="faq-h">Questions We <em>Love</em></h2></div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><span>How does simmmy's cosmic matching actually work?</span><span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">simmmy's superintelligent engine analyses 47 compatibility dimensions. It combines your full natal birth chart (sun, moon, rising, Venus, Mars), tarot Major Arcana archetype, numerology life path, destiny and soul urge numbers, psychological profile (attachment style, love language, Big Five, Enneagram), and real-time planetary transits. The result is the most comprehensive cosmic compatibility score ever built into a mobile app.</div></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><span>Do I need to believe in astrology to use simmmy?</span><span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Not at all — many of our most successful couples were sceptics. Astrology and tarot are one fascinating layer of our system. We also use rigorous psychological compatibility science. Even users who don't believe still report feeling more understood on simmmy than on any other dating app.</div></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><span>Is simmmy free to download?</span><span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Yes — simmmy is completely free to download on iOS and Android. The free plan includes daily curated matches and messaging. simmmy Premium unlocks unlimited matches, full cosmic reports, daily tarot readings, moon phase guidance, and event access. Premium starts from ₹299/month in India, £7.99 in the UK, and $9.99 in the US.</div></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><span>Is simmmy available in India?</span><span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Absolutely. simmmy is available in 189+ countries including India, which is one of our fastest-growing markets. Download from Google Play Store or Apple App Store today. Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu language options are coming in 2025.</div></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><span>How does simmmy keep me safe?</span><span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Safety is our top priority. Every profile is AI photo-verified. Our moderation system monitors 24/7. You can block or report any user instantly. Optional ID verification adds a trust layer. Your precise location is never shared with other users. All messages are end-to-end encrypted.</div></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><span>Can I use simmmy just to make friends?</span><span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Absolutely. simmmy's Friend Mode matches you with people for platonic connections — best friends, travel companions, business collaborators, creative partners. The same cosmic compatibility engine applies. Soul connections come in all forms, and simmmy honours all of them.</div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
